 may be engineered by strain in thin films\nand may find use in future applications of topological insulators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jul 2012 19:55:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Sep 2012 20:25:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
