dmill speed, redundancy between ST and SL would likely allow persistent\npattern to occur. Conversely, under dual constraint conditions, the absence of\nredundancy among SL, ST and SS would explain the generalized anti-persistent\npattern.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2012 09:18:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-24"}
