omerates,\nat very low energies for the $\\nu=5/2$, can be an interesting indication\nsupporting the validity of the anti-Pfaffian model in comparison to the\nPfaffian.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2012 10:20:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-17"}
